snippet.title: Mist Legacy - Alpha - Preparing for a fight!
snippet.description:
In  this video, a mid-level heroes is preparing his team for to explore one of the dangerous region of the game:

-Overview of the domain (home).

-Crafting new weapons to replace used ones.
-Preparing some potion and bandages.
-Checking for used items.
-And going to the region and fight the monsters!
